Why this works well
	•	Thread-safe: builder is stateless; ObjectMapper is reused safely.
	•	Dynamic placeholders: pass a map (placeholders) or just prefix context keys with ph. — no if/else per event.
	•	Extensible: add more fields in context (e.g., recipient.nameKana) and wire them into POJO later.
	•	Minimal mandatory checks to fail fast and push to DLQ when payload cannot be built.

